
We have used a local geth node and the online solidity compiler  / ethereum wallet

We will now move to use the truffle IDE and testrpc to give us a local test node



https://github.com/ConsenSys/truffle
to install do
http://truffle.readthedocs.io/en/latest/getting_started/installation/
npm install -g truffle

Documentation
http://truffle.readthedocs.io/en/latest/

Also install testrpc

https://github.com/ethereumjs/testrpc

TO create a project in an empty directory
type truffle init
this will create a dummy project for a crypto currency

the directory structure is as follows :
project
  \app
  \contracts
  \test
